### Verify Premium User and Anonymous Access to Posts (SQL)

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/docs/content/guides/local-development/testing/pgtap-extended.mdx

This test suite examines RLS behavior for premium content. It first authenticates as a 'premium_user' to confirm full access to all posts within a premium organization. Subsequently, it clears authentication to simulate an anonymous user and verifies that only free posts are visible, demonstrating RLS-based content gating.

```sql
-- Premium Content Access Tests
select tests.authenticate_as('premium_user');
select results_eq(
    $$select count(*) from posts where org_id = (select id from organizations where slug = 'premium-org')$$,
    ARRAY[3::bigint],
    'Premium user can see all posts'
);

select tests.clear_authentication();
select results_eq(
    $$select count(*) from posts where org_id = (select id from organizations where slug = 'premium-org')$$,
    ARRAY[2::bigint],
    'Anonymous users can only see free posts'
);
```

