### Write pgTAP Unit Tests for Supabase RLS with SQL

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/docs/content/guides/local-development/testing/overview.mdx

This SQL script uses pgTAP to test RLS policies by setting up test data and simulating user sessions. It verifies that users can only access and modify their own todos, ensuring proper RLS enforcement. The tests cover read and write operations.

```sql
begin;
-- install tests utilities
-- install pgtap extension for testing
create extension if not exists pgtap with schema extensions;
-- Start declare we'll have 4 test cases in our test suite
select plan(4);

-- Setup our testing data
